                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/2354" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-0370</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9608 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">绿动健康走——基于LBS的O2O场景营销</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Healthy Walking Program—An O2O Scene Marketing Show Case Based on LBS Tech</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王燕彦，崔春虎等</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国传媒大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">康师傅</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">24 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">茶饮料；O2O；场景营销；原生营销；2016百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Tea Drinks；O2O；Scene Marketing；Native Marketing</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">茶饮料是中国饮料市场的龙头产品之一。在经历了10多年的高速增长后，尤其在我国经济进入新常态的大背景下，茶饮料市场产能过剩也引发了增速放缓、业绩下滑的问题，有的品牌选择退出市场，有的品牌简单挣扎，而本案例的主角——康师傅茶饮品牌则积极创新，在深刻洞察消费市场变化的基础上，努力探索新的营销手段和模式，创造新的需求、寻求新的增长点。本案例介绍的是康师傅通过LBS等移动互联网技术，携手百度地图推出了“康师傅绿茶”步行健康走的活动，构建新的消费场景，配合线上线下相互导流的O2O手段，并设计社会化交互功能，邀请与品牌调性契合的明星代言，吸引消费者亲身参与，通过场景营销与原生营销，巧妙传递“康师傅=健康生活方式”的品牌价值，强化消费者的认同和共鸣，提升传播效果。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Tea drinks is one of the leading products of China&#39;s beverage market, After 10 years of rapid growing, especially in PRC economy go into the context of new normal, the market overcapacity of tea drinks has caused the producers have problem of declining performance and slowing growth,some brand quite the market and some struggle still, While The protagonist of our case—Kangshifu tea brand make innovation actively, upon the basis of profound insight into the consumer change of market, they try to explore new marketing means and mode that create new demand and seek new growth point. In this case Kangshifu cooperate with Baidu map to launch a campaign of “healthy walking program” which based on LBS tech of mobile internet .They deliver the brand image of “kangshifu equal to healthy life style” by scene marketing and native marketing:to build a new consumption scenarios, invite the film star which under the brand essence to represent this campaign , design social interaction and inspire consumer to join actively by all means of mutual diversion between online and offline .upon above efforts Kangshifu strengthen consumer&#39;s identity and resonance of brand, and improve communication effect at the same time.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2015</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《市场营销》、《创新管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字营销</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2016-08</td>
                            </tr>
